  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for avahi",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for avahi fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2021-26720: drop privileges when invoking avahi-daemon-check-dns.sh (bsc#1180827)\n- Update avahi-daemon-check-dns.sh from Debian. Our previous version relied on ifconfig, route, and init.d.\n- Add sudo to requires: used to drop privileges.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
